# Task 4: User & Permissions

## Objective

Restrict access to monitoring logs using a dedicated user.

---

## Steps

### 1. Create User

```bash
sudo adduser monitoruser
```

### 2. Assign Ownership

```bash
sudo chown -R monitoruser:monitoruser /opt/container-monitor
```

### 3. Set Permissions

```bash
sudo chmod -R 700 /opt/container-monitor
```

---

## Outcome

Only the monitoring user has access to logs, improving security.
